name: Monkey Eat Milkey
overview: An action game for one or two players by Ronny Nordqvist & Johan Janssen with music by Daniel Strandberg, together known as Software of Sweden, created for the RGCD C64 16KB Cartridge Game Development Competition 2012. Help the little monkey to eat his milk as fast as he can. By wiggling the joystick left and right you eat the milk. Don't forget to belch with the joystick up when necessary or something bad may happen. Best times saved to disk!
